document.full_text: on thursday cnn broadcast an on-camera interview with eman al-obeidy, a libyan lawyer who was dragged away from foreign journalists nearly two weeks ago, conducted in the office of saadi el-qaddafi, one of the libyan leaders sons.
document.title: the lede: video interview with woman who said she was raped by qaddafi forces
